# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Paddle Billing Configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# All Paddle secrets MUST be stored in .env.local (never committed to git).
# Copy the block below into your .env.local file and fill in the real values.
#
# HOW TO FIND EACH VALUE IN THE PADDLE DASHBOARD (app.paddle.com)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
#
# PADDLE_API_KEY
#   Developer Tools → Authentication → API Keys
#   Create a key with Read + Write permissions.
#   Value starts with "pdl_live_apikey_" (production) or "pdl_snd_apikey_" (sandbox).
#
# PADDLE_WEBHOOK_SECRET_KEY
#   Developer Tools → Webhooks → Add Destination
#   Endpoint URL: https://<your-domain>/api/paddle/webhook
#   Enable events: subscription.created, subscription.updated,
#                  subscription.canceled, transaction.completed,
#                  transaction.payment_failed
#   After saving, copy the "Secret key" (starts with "pdl_ntfset_").
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_CLIENT_TOKEN
#   Developer Tools → Authentication → Client-side tokens
#   Create a token — it starts with "live_" (production) or "test_" (sandbox).
#   This token is safe to expose to the browser (NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix).
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_ENVIRONMENT
#   Set to "sandbox" for local development / testing.
#   Set to "production" when you are ready to charge real money.
#
# PADDLE_ENVIRONMENT
#   Same as above but used server-side (webhook handler, checkout creation).
#   "sandbox" | "production"
#
# Paddle Price IDs  (Catalog → Products → <product> → Prices)
# -----------------------------------------------------------
# Create a "Pro" product with two prices ($12/mo and $96/yr) and an
# "Enterprise" product with two prices ($29/mo and $288/yr).
# Each Price ID starts with "pri_".
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_PRO_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID=pri_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_PRO_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=pri_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_ENTERPRISE_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID=pri_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_ENTERPRISE_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=pri_...
# PADDLE_API_KEY=pdl_live_apikey_...
# PADDLE_WEBHOOK_SECRET_KEY=pdl_ntfset_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_CLIENT_TOKEN=live_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PADDLE_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox
# PADDLE_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
